org.apache.uima.wikipedia.ae.parser
Class MWRevisionBuilder

java.lang.Object
  org.eclipse.mylyn.wikitext.core.parser.DocumentBuilder
      org.apache.uima.wikipedia.ae.parser.MWRevisionBuilder

public class MWRevisionBuilder
extends DocumentBuilder

This class is a helper for the actual parser. It acts as a sink for the parser events. It is used to notify the annotator for each new annotation, and also to build the revision's text without the wiki syntax.

Author:
Maxime Bury <Maxime.bury@gmail.com>
